1. Go to https://www.archlinux.org/mirrorlist/
2. Choose your settings.
3. Open "/etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist", preferably with gedit (gnome text editor).
4. Ctrl+A then Backspace -> Remove Everything
5. Copy Paste Generated List.
6. Remove the #'s before "Server". 
With gedit you can simple Ctrl+H...
Find="#Server"
Replace with="Server"

For Example

"
#Server = http://archlinux.cu.be/$repo/os/$arch
#Server = http://archlinux.mirror.kangaroot.net/$repo/os/$arch
"

to

"
Server = http://archlinux.cu.be/$repo/os/$arch
Server = http://archlinux.mirror.kangaroot.net/$repo/os/$arch
"



